-- MOVES-Martin Naville joins Stanhope Capital advisory board
-- 
-- Mon Oct 20, 2014 07:06AM EDT
-- None



Oct 20 (Reuters) - Global investment company Stanhope Capital said Martin Naville had joined its advisory board from Oct. 1.

Naville is the chief executive of the Swiss-American Chamber of Commerce, which facilitates business between the two countries. He is based in Switzerland.